<DOC>
<DOCNO>23363_11</DOCNO>
<TEXT>200 nautical miles (370 km) or to the edge of the continental margin
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>23363_12</DOCNO>
<TEXT>exclusive economic zone:
</TEXT>
